93
00:05:39,631 --> 00:05:41,675
There, see.
The scribbler understands.

94
00:05:41,716 --> 00:05:43,885
No, he's just a pervert!

95
00:05:43,927 --> 00:05:46,847
Well, sure, buying a
present sounds fine.

96
00:05:46,888 --> 00:05:50,267
But, uh, why a swimsuit
specifically?

97
00:05:50,308 --> 00:05:53,812
Oh, right. I suppose
you three wouldn't know.

98
00:05:53,854 --> 00:05:55,105
