101
00:05:59,943 --> 00:06:01,444
[YUKI]
Disgusting, Shigure.

102
00:06:01,486 --> 00:06:03,864
[TOHRU] I'm ready!
Sorry to keep you wait‐‐

103
00:06:03,905 --> 00:06:06,533
[SHIGURE]
Tohru! You have to, okay?

104
00:06:06,575 --> 00:06:08,994
Please get one.
For all our sakes!

105
00:06:09,035 --> 00:06:09,953
[TOHRU]
One what?

106
00:06:09,995 --> 00:06:10,787
Say yes!

107
00:06:10,829 --> 00:06:12,789
I'll get down on my knees
and beg if I have to!

108
00:06:12,831 --> 00:06:14,749
