weakness for Tohru, as well.

110
00:06:18,003 --> 00:06:19,546
[UOTANI]
Mh‐hm.

111
00:06:20,505 --> 00:06:22,132
[UOTANI sighs]

112
00:06:22,173 --> 00:06:25,010
[UOTANI] Deciding on one's gonna
be harder than I thought.

113
00:06:25,051 --> 00:06:27,178
