bother to ask us?!

154
00:07:50,011 --> 00:07:51,554
Why not? It was fun.

155
00:07:51,596 --> 00:07:54,349
Besides, there's no harm
in getting a second opinion.

156
00:07:54,391 --> 00:07:58,228
But Kyoko did think that
pink fit Tohru best.

157
00:07:58,269 --> 00:07:59,771
