the Crimson Butterfly,

159
00:08:02,023 --> 00:08:05,110
and that Tohru's dad, a
straightforward man, was white.

160
00:08:05,151 --> 00:08:08,488
Mix those, and you
get pink for Tohru.

161
00:08:08,530 --> 00:08:10,824
