Miss Honda. It shows.

164
00:08:16,454 --> 00:08:18,581
Helping her seems
to make you happy.

165
00:08:18,623 --> 00:08:19,666
[UOTANI]
Well, yeah.

166
00:08:19,708 --> 00:08:22,377
Like I told you before,
the girl kinda saved me.

167
00:08:22,419 --> 00:08:26,423
