Forever and ever.

194
00:09:25,690 --> 00:09:26,775
Oh, Tohru!

195
00:09:26,816 --> 00:09:28,526
Our Tohru.

196
00:09:28,568 --> 00:09:29,694
[YUKI, KYO]
Uh.

197
00:09:33,198 --> 00:09:35,617
[CLERK A]
Here's your table.

198
