go to the beach, right?

201
00:09:41,956 --> 00:09:44,709
[YUKI]
Mh‐hm. I hope so, anyway.

202
00:09:44,751 --> 00:09:47,545
We ladies should take a trip
of our own sometime, too.

203
00:09:47,587 --> 00:09:48,546
We should!

204
00:09:48,588 --> 00:09:50,131
