elementary school?

207
00:09:55,804 --> 00:09:58,139
Oh, no. Middle school, actually.

208
00:09:58,181 --> 00:10:00,517
Hanajima, you started at
our school back in what,

209
00:10:00,558 --> 00:10:01,226
eighth grade?

210
00:10:01,267 --> 00:10:04,020
