at my previous school.

212
00:10:06,898 --> 00:10:08,108
[BOTH]
Yeah?

213
00:10:08,149 --> 00:10:09,234
You were still part of the gang

214
00:10:09,275 --> 00:10:10,944
back when we first
met, weren't you?

215
00:10:10,985 --> 00:10:14,364
