with them in fifth grade.

216
00:10:14,405 --> 00:10:16,491
[TOHRU] You always went
around with a mask on.

217
00:10:16,533 --> 00:10:19,327
[UOTANI] Don't forget the long
skirts and super‐thin eyebrows.

218
00:10:19,369 --> 00:10:22,247
[HANAJIMA] No mask now, but
the last two are still true.

219
00:10:22,288 --> 00:10:23,873
[UOTANI]
Oh, yeah. Guess you're right.

220
00:10:23,915 --> 00:10:26,042
[UOTANI laughs]

221
