what to do with me.

227
00:10:39,347 --> 00:10:41,266
Neither did my dad.

228
00:10:41,307 --> 00:10:46,479
Seems like it should be harder,
but going bad's pretty easy.

229
00:10:46,521 --> 00:10:49,107
