know the half of it.

235
00:11:01,703 --> 00:11:04,414
Basically, I was a moron.

236
00:11:04,455 --> 00:11:08,334
An idiot of epic proportions.

237
00:11:08,376 --> 00:11:17,385
But still, even an idiot...
can find somebody to look up to.

238
00:11:17,427 --> 00:11:19,971
