and became a gang leader,

239
00:11:20,013 --> 00:11:21,764
despite being a woman.

240
00:11:21,806 --> 00:11:25,935
Her street name was
the Crimson Butterfly.

241
00:11:25,977 --> 00:11:28,146
Also known as Kyoko.

